{"tid":1463398,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"香港人口達752萬 較去年同期增1% 4.4萬人持單程證遷入","createTime":"2019-08-13T12:57:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T13:54:07.000Z","uid":53026,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"fa154bcbaf4b1a99ae125c3b72247047ba13aead","tid":1463398,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:57:19.000Z","msg":"香港人口達752萬 較去年同期增1% 4.4萬人持單程證遷入<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3154236/org/22163c045d7a255ff971917c8a0bfeab.jpg/RpYWkL2wkm7pGqRSjFn9ztLhjvfo-tt6TiSpZ04kqWc?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3154236%2Forg%2F22163c045d7a255ff971917c8a0bfeab.jpg%2FRpYWkL2wkm7pGqRSjFn9ztLhjvfo-tt6TiSpZ04kqWc%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=5634b2fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n社會新聞<br />\n撰文：袁澍<br />\n2019-08-13 17:28<br />\n最後更新日期：2019-08-13 17:28<br />\n<br />\n政府統計處今（13日）公布，今年年中香港人口臨時數字為752萬人，與去年同期人口比較增加了73,100人，增幅為1%。去年淨遷移人數為67,400人，其中44,400人為單程證持有人，佔其六成五。<br />\n政府統計處統計2019年年中香港人口臨時數字，香港人口數字首次突破750萬，較2018年中的745萬人口來比，共錄得73,100人增長，增長率為1%。（資料圖片）<br />\n<br />\n政府統計處統計2019年年中香港人口臨時數字，香港人口數字首次突破750萬，較2018年中的745萬人口來比，共錄得73,100人增長，增長率為1%。（資料圖片）<br />\n<br />\n政府統計處統計2019年年中香港人口臨時數字，香港人口數字首次突破750萬，較2018年中的745萬人口來比，共錄得73,100人增長，增長率為1%。當中人口自然增長（即出生減死亡）達5,700人，出生人數為53,300人，死亡人數為47,600人。在同期內，淨遷移人數為67,400人，其中44,400人為單程證持有人的移入，23,000人為其他香港居民的淨移入。<br />\n<br />\n香港人口是根據「居住人口」的定義而編製，包括「常住居民」和「流動居民」。二零一九年年中的總人口中，「常住居民」佔7,310,100人，而「流動居民」佔214,000人。根據慣例，每次發表最新的人口數字為臨時數字，經修訂的數字會在其後的六個月公布。"},{"pid":"a2dec94377fa6222a507e4ae4d2b1d6108385c8e","tid":1463398,"uid":114121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:59:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e2206fb1237a12d8f175557feb77785ec473c3c","tid":1463398,"uid":262389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:59:26.000Z","msg":"[緊急分析]法！不！責！眾！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1456781\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1456781</a>"},{"pid":"1758eb62dc5f77b2844c1458f03967eb260ad3d6","tid":1463398,"uid":53026,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:14:29.000Z","msg":"流動居民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fa3f312f045f95018342dd0c4de8a539f067529","tid":1463398,"uid":53026,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:15:31.000Z","msg":"唔知日日百幾二百人住邊呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7883e9759c9563d8cb5dce8a9c00a3ae65947500","tid":1463398,"uid":108016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:47:16.000Z","msg":"其他= 所謂專才"},{"pid":"3ff15208694a03442f03be5dfa8cb98b3ff794f4","tid":1463398,"uid":51920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:54:07.000Z","msg":"流動人口黎投票"}]}